headline.main: Red Bulls Spoil Atlanta Debut With 2-1 MLS Win
headline.print_headline: Red Bulls Spoil Atlanta Debut With 2-1 MLS Win

lead_paragraph: The New York Red Bulls scored two late goals to claim a 2-1 victory and spoil the Major League Soccer (MLS) debut of Atlanta United on Sunday.
